is forbidden.

277
00:21:09,456 --> 00:21:10,499
But still--

278
00:21:10,582 --> 00:21:11,750
"But still" is forbidden.

279
00:21:11,833 --> 00:21:13,835
It's an app test.
Do we have to go this far?

280
00:21:13,919 --> 00:21:17,464
And I told you. It's not "fall for me."
It's "fall in love with me."

281
00:21:17,964 --> 00:21:18,840
