282
00:21:20,592 --> 00:21:23,887
"Make Gi-tae fall in love with me!"

283
00:21:24,888 --> 00:21:26,139
Hey, "love"?

284
00:21:26,723 --> 00:21:29,684
This is so hard, seriously.

285
00:21:30,477 --> 00:21:32,062
Love is hard.

286
00:21:32,145 --> 00:21:34,356
You talk like you've been in love.

287
00:21:38,693 --> 00:21:41,947
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me.

288
00:21:42,030 --> 00:21:45,242
Please make Gi-tae fall in love with me!

289
00:21:46,827 --> 00:21:49,079
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me,

290
00:21:49,162 --> 00:21:50,872
no matter what!

291
00:22:01,508 --> 00:22:02,759
Sometimes, I…

292
00:22:03,260 --> 00:22:05,137
Actually, often, I get scared of you.

293
00:22:10,976 --> 00:22:11,810
Why's that?

294
00:22:12,310 --> 00:22:15,063
Because you know me way too well.

295
00:22:17,190 --> 00:22:19,401
Is me knowing you so well a bad thing?

296
00:22:24,739 --> 00:22:27,200
Do you know why people don't like my mom?

297
00:22:27,284 --> 00:22:29,703
She keeps seeing through…

298
00:22:31,913 --> 00:22:33,415
the things they want to hide.

299
00:22:35,167 --> 00:22:37,210
Everyone's got a lot they want to hide.

300
00:22:37,294 --> 00:22:39,171
For me, that's my home.

301
00:22:48,805 --> 00:22:50,182
I promised, didn't I?

302
00:22:50,765 --> 00:22:52,058
That I'd keep it secret.

303
00:22:52,142 --> 00:22:53,935
If I make you uncomfortable,

304
00:22:55,479 --> 00:22:57,314
I'll keep my distance at school.

305
00:23:04,070 --> 00:23:05,822
I don't know.

306
00:23:10,368 --> 00:23:12,913
But this secret is no joke either.

307
00:23:12,996 --> 00:23:15,290
-Hey, delete that right now.
-No way.

308
00:23:15,373 --> 00:23:16,208
Delete it.

309
00:23:16,291 --> 00:23:18,919
-No way.
-Come on, not cool.

310
00:23:19,002 --> 00:23:20,712
-Come on.
-Hurry up and go to sleep.

311
00:23:20,795 --> 00:23:22,005
Let's go to sleep. Now.

312
00:23:22,589 --> 00:23:24,049
-Let's sleep.
-You need to…

313
00:23:24,132 --> 00:23:26,676
-Go to sleep.
-I'm not sleeping until you delete it.

314
00:23:30,013 --> 00:23:33,141
That app you made… Girigo, was it?
I think it'll win first place.

315
00:23:33,225 --> 00:23:36,019
-Really?
-Yeah. It's simple but super fun.

316
00:23:36,520 --> 00:23:37,812
After making my wish,

317
00:23:37,896 --> 00:23:40,106
my heart's racing,
like it's gonna come true.

318
00:23:41,066 --> 00:23:42,692
And the best part was

319
00:23:43,193 --> 00:23:44,819
