Every time? What kind of "every time"?

324
00:24:00,961 --> 00:24:01,878
You get this, right?

325
00:24:01,962 --> 00:24:03,838
And what is an "article"? An article.

326
00:24:03,922 --> 00:24:06,716
"Every time we read an article
on the Internet."

327
00:24:06,800 --> 00:24:08,927
But is that a complete sentence? Not yet.

328
00:24:09,010 --> 00:24:11,137
