338
00:24:41,167 --> 00:24:43,253
Yeah. Can we order anything here?

339
00:24:50,635 --> 00:24:52,846
Maybe the wish is actually working.

340
00:24:52,929 --> 00:24:55,098
I made eye contact with Gi-tae
twice today.

341
00:24:55,599 --> 00:24:57,851
See? I told you it works.

342
00:24:59,185 --> 00:25:00,812
