350
00:25:18,246 --> 00:25:20,498
I said I'm not selling! Why cause a scene?

351
00:25:20,582 --> 00:25:22,042
What would you fucking know?

352
00:25:22,125 --> 00:25:23,501
Why come here all drunk?

353
00:25:23,585 --> 00:25:25,754
