-Let go! Now!

354
00:25:25,837 --> 00:25:27,255
Get out of my way!

355
00:25:27,339 --> 00:25:30,091
SI-WON, DON'T STRESS TOO MUCH…
YOUR MOM…

356
00:25:39,684 --> 00:25:43,938
I'M AT THE HIDEOUT. WHEN ARE YOU COMING?

357
00:26:00,455 --> 00:26:01,498
Hey, have you had…

358
00:26:01,581 --> 00:26:02,707
Hey.

359
00:26:03,208 --> 00:26:04,376
Dear me.

360
00:26:05,418 --> 00:26:08,046
Even your friend treats me better
than you do.

361
00:26:10,298 --> 00:26:11,132
Have you…

362
00:26:13,134 --> 00:26:14,636
My goodness. Damn it.

363
00:26:24,396 --> 00:26:27,232
I MIGHT JUST SLEEP AT HOME TONIGHT!
SEE YOU TOMORROW!

364
00:26:36,741 --> 00:26:41,037
I MIGHT JUST SLEEP AT HOME TONIGHT!
SEE YOU TOMORROW!

365
00:27:06,563 --> 00:27:08,106
What the heck?

366
00:27:19,409 --> 00:27:20,618
Goodness me.

367
00:28:39,989 --> 00:28:41,282
Hair.

368
00:28:41,366 --> 00:28:42,534
My daughter's hair.

369
00:28:46,538 --> 00:28:47,664
SEORIN

370
00:28:56,297 --> 00:28:58,299
My daughter, Si-won.

371
00:28:58,383 --> 00:29:00,134
My daughter, Si-won, please…

372
00:29:01,886 --> 00:29:04,305
Heavenly spirit, I'm sorry.

373
00:29:04,806 --> 00:29:08,017
I'm sorry. The foolish child didn't know
what she was doing.

374
00:29:08,101 --> 00:29:09,435
I pray to the Bulsa Jeseok.

375
00:29:09,519 --> 00:29:11,813
Please punish me instead of my daughter.

376
00:29:11,896 --> 00:29:15,400
Please punish me
instead of my daughter, Si-won.

377
00:29:15,483 --> 00:29:18,069
I pray to Hwangsa Jebul and Bulsa Jeseok.

378
00:29:18,903 --> 00:29:22,323
Please accept my sincerity
and forgive my daughter, Si-won.

379
00:30:10,538 --> 00:30:12,832
The call could not be connected.

380
00:30:55,416 --> 00:30:56,250
Hye-ryung!

381
00:31:05,093 --> 00:31:06,386
Wait.

382
00:31:07,845 --> 00:31:10,765
You have to listen to me carefully.

383
00:31:12,183 --> 00:31:18,064
Put this amulet on Si-won or in her bag
without her knowing, no matter what.

384
00:31:18,147 --> 00:31:21,150
That girl takes after her father,

385
00:31:21,234 --> 00:31:23,653
so I'm sure just seeing an amulet
will freak her out.

386
00:31:24,529 --> 00:31:27,490
Still, you have to put it in
without her noticing.

387
00:31:28,282 --> 00:31:33,287
I couldn't save my husband,
but I have to save my child at least.

388
00:31:34,247 --> 00:31:35,206
Okay?

389
00:31:35,289 --> 00:31:37,959
Why aren't you answering? Huh?

390
00:31:41,879 --> 00:31:43,631
You should go to the hospital first.

391
00:31:47,010 --> 00:31:50,972
You saw how I fixed your eye, right?

392
00:31:51,472 --> 00:31:55,351
I'll take care of myself,
so you hurry and go to Si-won, okay?

393
00:31:58,730 --> 00:31:59,897
Get out of here!

394
00:32:03,609 --> 00:32:04,819
Go! Now!

395
00:32:05,319 --> 00:32:07,321
Hurry! Go now!

396
00:32:07,822 --> 00:32:09,282
Go! Now!

397
00:32:41,606 --> 00:32:42,690
Si-won.

398
00:32:43,649 --> 00:32:45,568
-Today, at your place--
-What?

399
00:32:53,701 --> 00:32:54,660
