403
00:33:14,013 --> 00:33:16,516
The Road Away by Kim So-wol.

404
00:33:17,141 --> 00:33:20,019
The thought of saying I miss you
Only makes me miss you more

405
00:33:20,812 --> 00:33:24,190
Perhaps I should just leave
And yet, once again…

406
00:33:24,941 --> 00:33:28,277
That girl takes after her father,

407
00:33:29,278 --> 00:33:32,698
so I'm sure just seeing an amulet
will freak her out.

408
00:33:33,574 --> 00:33:36,494
Still, you have to put it in
without her noticing.

409
00:33:37,286 --> 00:33:42,291
I couldn't save my husband,
but I have to save my child at least.

410
00:33:43,251 --> 00:33:44,210
Okay?

411
00:33:44,293 --> 00:33:47,046
There are crows on that mountain
And crows in the field

412
00:33:47,880 --> 00:33:51,259
They caw as the sun sets
Over the western hills

413
00:33:51,759 --> 00:33:52,593
The river…

414
00:34:02,436 --> 00:34:03,271
Seriously.

415
00:34:03,354 --> 00:34:05,106
Be right back.

416
00:34:05,189 --> 00:34:06,274
I'll come with you.

417
00:34:10,069 --> 00:34:10,903
Hey.

418
00:34:13,406 --> 00:34:14,699
What are you doing?

419
00:34:31,924 --> 00:34:33,050
This morning, your mom--

420
00:35:18,429 --> 00:35:19,931
It was freaking crazy.

421
00:35:20,014 --> 00:35:23,517
She slapped Do Hye-ryung
and tore the amulet to shreds.

422
00:35:23,601 --> 00:35:25,603
That's creepy as hell. Just wow.

423
00:35:25,686 --> 00:35:27,063
Doesn't something feel off?

424
00:35:27,146 --> 00:35:29,065
She avoids talking about Do Hye-ryung,

425
00:35:29,148 --> 00:35:31,234
