whenever shamanism comes up.

426
00:35:31,817 --> 00:35:34,237
Maybe Kwon Si-won's the one
connected to the shaman.

427
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:35,655
Well,

428
00:35:36,197 --> 00:35:38,908
