430
00:35:42,036 --> 00:35:43,829
But maybe I just misheard her.

431
00:35:45,164 --> 00:35:46,207
What did she say?

432
00:35:46,290 --> 00:35:47,833
Just spit it out.

433
00:35:47,917 --> 00:35:49,168
Well,

434
00:35:50,211 --> 00:35:53,256
Do Hye-ryung was being really careful
with Si-won, and…

435
00:35:53,339 --> 00:35:54,715
Fucking Do Hye-ryung.

436
00:35:54,799 --> 00:35:56,926
"This morning, your mom--"

437
00:35:59,387 --> 00:36:00,513
You're here.

438
00:36:07,019 --> 00:36:08,312
Come check it out.

439
00:36:08,813 --> 00:36:10,064
Our entry for this contest.

440
00:36:10,147 --> 00:36:12,024
