-That was quick.

441
00:36:13,567 --> 00:36:14,986
How did you pull this off?

442
00:36:15,069 --> 00:36:18,030
Isn't the design a bit too dark?

443
00:36:18,990 --> 00:36:19,824
I like it.

444
00:36:20,324 --> 00:36:22,493
Of course you like it.
You didn't do a thing.

445
00:36:24,954 --> 00:36:28,291
None of you did anything. Don't you agree?

446
00:36:29,125 --> 00:36:29,959
But still…

447
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:35,923
All you did was run your mouth,
but you came up with the design idea.

448
00:36:37,091 --> 00:36:40,678
And you talked mad smack behind my back,

449
00:36:41,762 --> 00:36:43,222
but you brought up shamanism.

450
00:36:46,392 --> 00:36:49,312
Gi-tae, you haven't contributed at all,

451
00:36:50,896 --> 00:36:52,440
so help me with this.

452
00:37:29,477 --> 00:37:30,436
Hey.

453
00:37:30,936 --> 00:37:32,605
Have you heard of Girigo…

454
00:37:32,688 --> 00:37:33,522
What?

455
00:37:36,525 --> 00:37:38,778
Have you heard of an app
that grants wishes?

456
00:37:39,278 --> 00:37:40,446
What are you saying?

457
00:37:42,323 --> 00:37:45,159
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me.

458
00:37:45,242 --> 00:37:46,077
What's that?

459
00:37:46,160 --> 00:37:49,997
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me,
no matter what!

460
00:37:50,081 --> 00:37:52,666
Hey, what's up with her?

461
00:37:52,750 --> 00:37:54,794
That's gotta be embarrassing!

462
00:37:54,877 --> 00:37:58,506
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me,
no matter what!

463
00:38:06,555 --> 00:38:09,809
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me,
no matter what!

464
00:38:09,892 --> 00:38:11,394
Hey, it's in the group chat.

465
00:38:11,477 --> 00:38:12,395
Hey, what's this?

466
00:38:15,106 --> 00:38:16,690
Damn! So freaking embarrassing.

467
00:38:17,608 --> 00:38:20,152
Please make Gi-tae fall in love with me!

468
00:38:22,405 --> 00:38:25,282
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me.

469
00:38:26,617 --> 00:38:30,454
Make Gi-tae fall in love with me,
no matter what!

470
00:38:32,623 --> 00:38:33,457
Hey.

471
00:38:34,250 --> 00:38:35,376
Shamanism.

472
00:38:36,085 --> 00:38:37,420
Accept her confession!

473
00:38:38,045 --> 00:38:40,131
You really are a crazy shaman's daughter.

474
00:38:40,214 --> 00:38:42,550
How can you believe that crap? Huh?

475
00:38:48,597 --> 00:38:51,517
Man, you've got shit for brains.

476
00:38:51,600 --> 00:38:53,936
Shit, you hear me? Huh?

477
00:38:54,895 --> 00:38:55,938
Hey, stop filming.

478
00:38:56,021 --> 00:38:57,064
It's fine.

479
00:38:57,815 --> 00:38:58,649
Hey.

480
00:38:58,732 --> 00:39:01,402
What makes you think
you can confess to me?

481
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:05,281
Why the glare?

482
00:39:05,364 --> 00:39:07,450
And you want me to love who?
You crazy bitch!

483
00:39:18,127 --> 00:39:18,961
Got a death wish?

484
00:39:31,182 --> 00:39:32,016
Is that enough?

485
00:39:56,874 --> 00:39:57,708
HAN GI-TAE

486
00:40:00,544 --> 00:40:03,631
Take something that belongs
to the person you want to grab by deolmi.

487
00:40:04,340 --> 00:40:07,384
Preferably their nails, toenails, or hair.

488
00:40:08,636 --> 00:40:10,930
Tie that thing to the doll
with the silk thread.

489
00:40:13,057 --> 00:40:14,975
Then carve out the eyes, nose,
and mouth on the face,

490
00:40:15,726 --> 00:40:18,229
write down their saju here,

491
00:40:19,897 --> 00:40:23,067
and spray it all over
until the silk thread turns red…

492
00:40:25,528 --> 00:40:27,321
-Spray what?
-Blood.

493
00:40:27,404 --> 00:40:30,491
Warm, fresh blood
that still has life in it.

494
00:40:33,661 --> 00:40:35,913
MARCH 12, 2005
DO HYE-RYUNG

495
00:40:45,965 --> 00:40:49,343
I told you. Not just anyone can do it
just by copying the steps.

496
00:40:50,010 --> 00:40:51,887
What matters more is…

497
00:40:52,513 --> 00:40:54,557
An innate gift?

498
00:40:54,640 --> 00:40:56,267
Yes, that's also important.

499
00:40:56,350 --> 00:40:58,852
But what's more important than that

500
00:40:59,562 --> 00:41:00,813
is one's heart.

501
00:41:02,439 --> 00:41:03,857
According to the scriptures,

502
00:41:03,941 --> 00:41:06,986
simwibeopbon simjonsimsa.

503
00:41:07,486 --> 00:41:10,322
In other words,
the mind is the root and master

504
00:41:10,406 --> 00:41:11,657
of all things.

505
00:41:13,284 --> 00:41:16,704
To control one arm,

506
00:41:17,204 --> 00:41:19,498
