507
00:41:21,250 --> 00:41:23,669
To control two arms,

508
00:41:23,752 --> 00:41:26,088
you need to offer up at least a pig.

509
00:41:26,797 --> 00:41:28,424
Have you ever heard that…

510
00:41:31,218 --> 00:41:33,512
if you write down your saju
and make a wish…

511
00:41:36,098 --> 00:41:36,974
it'll come true?

512
00:41:38,058 --> 00:41:39,226
Yes, that's right.

513
00:41:41,270 --> 00:41:43,564
I'll make the wish
just the way you told me.

514
00:41:45,107 --> 00:41:46,358
My wish is…

515
00:41:55,242 --> 00:41:56,619
for all of you to die.

516
00:42:08,130 --> 00:42:09,381
That's my wish.

517
00:42:23,395 --> 00:42:25,648
Hey, Kwon Si-won! Did you see the video?

518
00:42:26,148 --> 00:42:27,858
Delete it before anyone sees it!

519
00:42:28,359 --> 00:42:30,611
This shit happened
because you asked me to help!

520
00:42:31,820 --> 00:42:33,989
I'll destroy the entire server
if I have to,

521
00:42:34,073 --> 00:42:36,033
so shut the hell up!

522
00:42:46,835 --> 00:42:49,380
DELETE FOLDER

523
00:42:51,048 --> 00:42:52,132
Damn it!

